migrateCP(address,uint256,uint256,bool,u.details: If the pool with the current conditions doesn't exist it will be deployed.

params.amount: Liquidity amount (Lp token balance) to be migrated.
params.currentPool: Trident CP pool address we want to migrate from. Can be form an outdated CP factory.
params.minLpReceived: Slippage protection for minting liquidity on the Trident CP pool.
params.minToken0Received: Slippage protection for removing liquidity. Values are in BentoBox shares.
params.minToken1Received: Slippage protection for removing liquidity. Values are in BentoBox shares.
params.swapFee: Swap fee of the Trident CP pool we are migrating into.
params.twapSupport: Whether the Trident CP pool we are migrating into supports twap oracles.

migrateLegacyToCP(address,uint256,uint25.details: If the pool with the current conditions doesn't exist it will be deployed.

params.amount: Liquidity amount (Lp token balance) to be migrated.
params.minLpReceived: Slippage protection for minting liquidity on the Trident CP pool.
params.minToken0Received: Slippage protection for removing liquidity from a UniV2 style pool.
params.minToken1Received: Slippage protection for removing liquidity from a UniV2 style pool.
params.pair: Uniswap V2 style liquidity pool address.
params.swapFee: Swap fee of the Trident CP pool we are migrating into.
params.twapSupport: Whether the Trident CP pool we are migrating into supports twap oracles.

migrateCP(address,uint256,uint256,bool,u.notice: Function to migrate betewwn Trident CP pools with different fee / twap settings.

migrateLegacyToCP(address,uint256,uint25.notice: Function to migrate existing Sushiswap or other Uniswap V2 style pools to Trident.

userdoc.notice: Liquidity migrator from UniV2 style pool to Trident Constant product pool.
